&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In the woods&lt;/strong&gt; - is a five caches series placed near a paved trail through the forest that connects Gavana neighborhood with Baloteşti village. The route can be done by car or bike.&lt;/p&gt;<br />
&lt;p&gt;Not far away, &lt;strong&gt;Baloteşti Cemetery&lt;/strong&gt; is placed in a glance.&lt;br /&gt;     From here, the road forks: one part leads to Baloteşti village and the other joins Zamfireşti street.&lt;/p&gt;
<p><em>This <a href='http://www.opencaching.ro/viewcache.php?cacheid=52'>geocache</a> description comes from the <a href='http://www.opencaching.ro/'>Opencaching.RO</a> site.</em></p>

&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;In the woods&lt;/strong&gt; - is a five caches series placed near a paved trail through the forest that connects Găvana neighborhood with Baloteşti village. The route can be done by car or bike.&lt;/p&gt;<br />
&lt;p&gt;After a couple of hills and valleys, you can stop to rest in &lt;strong&gt;Grigoreşti glade&lt;/strong&gt;. The view is beautiful and you can also search for a cache. &lt;br /&gt; The Pitesti people come here to relax on the green grass, to eat barbecue and listen to music out loud from the stereo of their car. Don't ask me why.&lt;/p&gt;
<p><em>This <a href='http://www.opencaching.ro/viewcache.php?cacheid=53'>geocache</a> description comes from the <a href='http://www.opencaching.ro/'>Opencaching.RO</a> site.</em></p>

&lt;p style=&quot;text-align: center;&quot;&gt;Children from all over town go out to play.&lt;br /&gt;The Tulip is there to watch.&lt;br /&gt;In the beautiful Spring day, we all have fun.&lt;br /&gt;The Tulip is there, among them all.&lt;br /&gt;Day and night, the joy never ends.&lt;br /&gt;Children come from near and far.&lt;br /&gt;Everybody jumps and plays all day long.&lt;br /&gt;There is no sign of rain.&lt;br /&gt;Spring makes us happy again.&lt;br /&gt;And there she is, having fun, the Mysterious Tulip.&lt;br /&gt;Among the children she's feeling great.&lt;br /&gt;The Tulip is the happiest of them all.&lt;br /&gt;And everybody is hopping around.&lt;br /&gt;They are all having fun in the parc.&lt;br /&gt;Endless happiness is in the air.&lt;/p&gt;<br />
&lt;div style=&quot;text-align: center; margin-top: 1em;&quot;&gt;&lt;img src=&quot;http://laleaua.opencaching.ro/page/2014/files/topaiala.png&quot; alt=&quot;&quot; /&gt;&lt;/div&gt;
<p><em>This <a href='http://www.opencaching.ro/viewcache.php?cacheid=59'>geocache</a> description comes from the <a href='http://www.opencaching.ro/'>Opencaching.RO</a> site.</em></p>

&lt;h3&gt;The Tulip and the Raspberry&lt;/h3&gt;<br />
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span id=&quot;ctl00_ContentBody_LongDescription&quot;&gt;&lt;br /&gt; If you found the mysterious star (&quot;Steaua Misterioasă&quot;), the you can easily guess L.&lt;br /&gt; Depending on how well do you &quot;exercise&quot; your skills, the S is no mystery.&lt;br /&gt; &lt;strong&gt;N44 51.{L}6 E24 51.8{S}&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
<p><em>This <a href='http://www.opencaching.ro/viewcache.php?cacheid=60'>geocache</a> description comes from the <a href='http://www.opencaching.ro/'>Opencaching.RO</a> site.</em></p>
